$interpreted: Male Demihuman: Wah! We beat Yamitsuki!
Male Demihuman: We can go get a prize~
Yamitsuki: ...Be careful not to fall.
Bandit Leader: Very keen, "Miss Yamitsuki". Not even the slightest bit of maliciousness passes by you unnoticed...
Yamitsuki: ...You're...a bandit?
Bandit Leader: That's right. You took good care of my boys.
Bandit Leader: No need for me to remind you. You've probably already found out that my gang has infiltrated the crowd.
Bandit Leader: If you try to make a sound, what gets scattered on the ground won't be water, but the fresh blood of unknowing demihumans...
Yamitsuki: ...You want the kingdom treasures, I'm assuming. Then don't make a move against them.
Bandit Leader: Oh, that's what you think?
Bandit Leader: Unfortunately, you guessed wrong...the treasures aren't our target.
Bandit Leader: What I want...is you.
Yamitsuki: .........
Bandit Leader: Surprised? Not many people these days know the value of a member of the Feather Clan. Luckily, I'm one of them.
Bandit Leader: Compared to you, a few chests of treasure are nothing.
Yamitsuki: ...I've seen many like you.
Yamitsuki: Not one has succeeded. Neither will you.
Bandit Leader: Hehe...So that's how it is? You must realize that for someone like me, there's no limit to my persistence and desire.
Female Demihuman: Ah, Miss Yamitsuki! Your performance was amazing!
Yamitsuki: .........
Female Demihuman: ...Miss Yamitsuki? What's wrong...
Yamitsuki: ...N-Nothing...
Yamitsuki: Carry on with the fun.
Female Demihuman: Okay! You too!
Bandit Leader: Very good. Good girl, Miss Yamitsuki.
Bandit Leader: Okay, let's go...be careful not to be discovered.
Yamitsuki: .........
Nigel: Yamitsuki...? Her expression...
Nigel: ...That woman!
Leah: Tricked! Looks like that woman and the bandits are working together...
Fredrica: By the look on her face, she's unable to make a move, don't you think?
Fredrica: If everyone here is that woman's hostage and she makes a move, the whole fair will be annihilated...
Nigel: Damn...
Izumi: Hmm...well we've got quite the brilliant plan. Not only can we save Yamitsuki, it won't affect the fair.
Nigel: Really?
Izumi: Relax. This time, I won't trick you~
Nigel: W-What are you doing with those clothes...?
Izumi: How far are you willing to go for her?
Izumi: Let's see...Nigel!
Bandit Leader: Tsk, better listen. If we stay deadlocked, that'd be unacceptable. Looks like I'll have to slaughter a few demihumans to make you come with me...
Yamitsuki: ...Stop, otherwise I'll...
Bandit Leader: Haha, now you're threatening me?
Bandit Leader: With your abilities, you can surely take me in a brawl. But I'm well aware that you don't wish to see your comrades' blood spilled...
Bandit Leader: Even if just one or two demihumans die, you'll never forgive yourself.
Yamitsuki: ...*gasp*...
Bandit Leader: Let's see...yes. Let's start with that brat, shall we?
Yamitsuki: N-No...!
???: Hold it right there!
Bandit Leader: What!?
Yamitsuki: ......!
Male Demihuman: Hey, what's going on over there?
Female Demihuman: Some strange figure appeared...
Female Demihuman: Ey, why does that figure look familiar?
Yamitsuki: ...Wait, don't startle everyone!
Yamitsuki: It was so hard to get everyone to relax...
Nigel: I am justice incarnate: The Masked Marauder! Today, I'm here to eradicate evil!
Female Demihuman: Didn't think there'd be a secret performance! The humans really put their all into this!
Yamitsuki: ...Is that so?
Nigel: ──Of course not!!
Bandit Leader: Who are you? Why are you meddling in our affairs!?
Nigel: ...You ask me who I am?
Bandit Leader: Stop! Don't come any closer!
Nigel: You ask me why I interfere in your affairs?
Bandit Leader: I-I said don't come closer!
Nigel: She's family to me! And she...is the most important person in my life!
Nigel: ──That's why!!
Yamitsuki: .........!
Bandit Leader: On y-y-your hand, that's...
Leah: That's a super-duper easter egg, created by yours truly~
Leah: Show her who's boss, Masked Marauder!!
Bandit Leader: Damn, don't think about running...
Fredrica: Aigh-ya, finally the good guy sticks his head out~
Fredrica: How can we let that floosie ruin it?
Bandit Leader: What the hell are you talking about?
Bandit Leader: You made me do this! Just wait for the blood-spilling dance of the demihumans!
Bandit Leader: Now!!!
Bandit Leader: ...Wh-What? Why did no one respond!?
Fredrica: Babe, how naive? Horn boy over there isn't the only good guy I was referring to~
Jerome: Well then, all the bandits have been beaten down. All thanks to you sniffing out their odor, Young Lio.
Lio: It was n-nothing.
Lio: Sh-Should we go help my sister and them?
Jerome: No, the general doesn't want to startle the crowd.
Jerome: That's why Nigel showed up dressed like that.
Jerome: That way everyone would think it was just part of the performance. They'll take care of that bandit woman.
Lio: Mr. Jerome...how'd you know?
Jerome: How'd I know...?
Jerome: Even though I didn't see it in her eyes, we established a mutual understanding a long time ago.
Lio: So cool...I want to be like Mr. Jerome when I grow up!
Bandit Leader: Bastards! Useless rats!
Izumi: Wanna run? There's nowhere to go~
Fredrica: If I let you go, my vacation is ruined~
Leah: Hehe, this time I'll help~
Leah: Tie 'er up! Trying to hurt everyone, you rotten hag!
Fredrica: Bunny-boo!
Leah: Yes, ma'am!
Bandit Leader: ...*cough*...*cough*...damn you! Next time, I won't let you go!!
Male Demihuman: Wah~brilliant! What a magnificent performance!
Female Demihuman: These humans are amazing!
Leah: Seeing everyone happy is such a great feeling~
Fredrica: Aigh-ya, handsome, bunny boy, what are you doing zoning out over there?
Fredrica: Wanna come up?
Jerome: No, General...
Jerome: The hard work is all thanks to you and those beside you. As your officer, I am delighted for you.
Fredrica: Yes~perfect answer.
Fredrica: Worth falling for...
Jerome: ...G-General, what are you saying?
